            <div class="row">
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-gears"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p>The site is so simply you can use it while checking your other 20 sites or just use our site becuase we made it that easy.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-compass"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Discover Interest</h3>
                    <p>Nfuse allows you to find all the things that you might find cool or discover new worlds that your missing out on.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-image"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Share Photos</h3>
                    <p>Share a photo to the world of what you like or just post as many selfies as you possibly can for the rest of your life.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-users"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Follow Friends</h3>
                    <p>Remove the digital walls and view what everyone is posting on all social media.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-star"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Popular Media</h3>
                    <p>We have the most popular media from all different social media site.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-search"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Social Search</h3>
                    <p>Use our powerful seach engine to discover trendy social media post.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-compress"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Content Mashup</h3>
                    <p>We have over eight social media site that you can easily view in a single feed.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-eye"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Exclusive Posts</h3>
                    <p>Follow someone a see exclusive post that you can not see anywhere else.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-icon col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                    <i class="outlined fa fa-map-signs"></i>
                    <h3 class="light">Explore Categories</h3>
                    <p>We created popular categories so you can easily explore the most popular social media.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden-xs col-xs-12">
                    <a href="#steps" class="btn btn-lg btn-default page-scroll animated">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
                <div class="visible-xs col-xs-12 text-center">
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-default signuptoggler animated">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg"></div>
    </section>

